**RECURSIVE Code (will give TLE for large testcases):**
```
public int combinationSum4(int[] nums, int target) {
    if (target == 0) {
        return 1;
    }
    int count = 0;
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {
        if (nums [i] <= target)
            count += combinationSum4 (nums, target - nums [i]);
    }
    return count;
}
```

**DP (MEMOIZATION) of the above Recursive Code:**
```
class Solution {
    public int dp [];

    public int combinationSum4 (int[] nums, int target) {
        dp = new int [target + 1];
        Arrays.fill (dp, -1);
        return Solve (nums, target);
    }

    public int Solve (int nums [], int sum) {
        if (sum == 0)
            return 1;
        if (sum < 0)
            return 0;
        if (dp [sum] != -1)
            return dp [sum];
        int count = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {
            if (nums [i] <= sum)
                count += Solve (nums, sum - nums [i]);
        }
        return dp [sum] = count;
    }
}
```

